zaibatsu.1.t: "The Corporate Empire"
zaibatsu.1.d: "The enduring partnership between the [ROOT.GetCountry.GetAdjective] state and the [SCOPE.gsInterestGroup('zaibatsu_ig').GetName] has cemented the power of the conglomerates within [SCOPE.GetRootScope.GetCountry.GetCustom('country_legislature_name')]. The politicians may govern, but the generals and executives will rule."
zaibatsu.1.f: "[SCOPE.sCharacter('pm_scope').GetFullNameNoFormatting] looked down upon the bout from [SCOPE.sCharacter('pm_scope').GetHerHis] covered box. [SCOPE.sCharacter('pm_scope').GetHerHis|U] preferred wrestler's opponent had pushed [SCOPE.sCharacter('pm_scope').GetHerHis] champion to the very edge of the rice-straw ring, and [SCOPE.sCharacter('pm_scope').GetSheHe] had found [SCOPE.sCharacter('pm_scope').GetHerselfHimself] struggling to keep [SCOPE.sCharacter('pm_scope').GetHerHis] knuckles from going white. At the Prime Minister's side, perfectly serene, stood [SCOPE.sCharacter('relevant_zaibatsu_exec').GetFullNameNoFormatting].\n\nThe referee pointed his fan, and cheer rose from the lower seats. A rain of seat cushions flew through the air, showering the ring. [SCOPE.sCharacter('relevant_zaibatsu_exec').GetFirstNameNoFormatting] turned his head towards [SCOPE.sCharacter('pm_scope').GetFirstNameNoFormatting], and smiled. There, on the far side of the ring, stamped into one of the walls, was the #italic mon#! of [SCOPE.sCompany('relevant_zaibatsu').GetNameNoFormatting]."
zaibatsu.1.a: "Let [ROOT.GetCountry.GetCapital.GetCityHubName] unfold like a sea of light."
zaibatsu.1.b: "Our supply chain could always be more secure."

zaibatsu.2.t: "Locked Down"
zaibatsu.2.t_1: "The Leveling Hand"
zaibatsu.2.d: "The efforts of the [SCOPE.sCharacter('pm_scope').GetLastName] cabinet have curtailed the abilities of the [SCOPE.gsInterestGroup('zaibatsu_ig').GetName] to exert control over [SCOPE.GetRootScope.GetCountry.GetCustom('country_legislature_name')]. The politicians will rule, and the executives shall focus on their profits."
zaibatsu.2.d_1: "The [SCOPE.sCharacter('pm_scope').GetLastName] cabinet's policies of free trade have eroded the network of military-industrial contracts key to the [SCOPE.gsInterestGroup('zaibatsu_ig').GetName]'s control over [SCOPE.GetRootScope.GetCountry.GetCustom('country_legislature_name')]. The politicians will rule, and the executives shall focus on their profits."
zaibatsu.2.f: "A flock of executives filtered into the uppermost meeting room of the [SCOPE.sCompany('relevant_zaibatsu').GetNameNoFormatting] headquarters. [SCOPE.sCharacter('name_a_scope').GetFirstNameNoFormatting] was third to enter, after the secretaries. [SCOPE.sCharacter('name_a_scope').GetSheHe|U] took [SCOPE.sCharacter('name_a_scope').GetHerHis] seat by the door, and watched [SCOPE.sCharacter('name_a_scope').GetHerHis] seniors pass by. A weak trickle of steam wafted off the cup of tea before [SCOPE.sCharacter('name_a_scope').GetHerHim].\n\n[SCOPE.sCharacter('relevant_zaibatsu_exec').GetFullNameNoFormatting] was the last to enter. [SCOPE.sCharacter('relevant_zaibatsu_exec').GetHerHis|U] gaze passed over each of [SCOPE.sCharacter('relevant_zaibatsu_exec').GetHerHis] employees in turn. There was a look in [SCOPE.sCharacter('relevant_zaibatsu_exec').GetHerHis] eyes, [SCOPE.sCharacter('name_a_scope').GetFirstNameNoFormatting] noticed, one that the Baron had never shown before. Exhaustion. The shadows cast on [SCOPE.sCharacter('relevant_zaibatsu_exec').GetHerHis] face seemed deeper than before, and [SCOPE.sCharacter('relevant_zaibatsu_exec').GetHerHis] silver hair ever thinner."
zaibatsu.2.a: "Sovereign power is ours alone."
zaibatsu.2.b: "Let the people know—[SCOPE.GetRootScope.GetCountry.GetCustom('country_legislature_name')] will not be bought."

